*xbox-sources-2.4.26-r4 (05 Aug 2004)

  05 Aug 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> -xbox-sources-2.4.26-r3.ebuild,
  +xbox-sources-2.4.26-r4.ebuild, -xbox-sources-2.6.7-r3.ebuild,
  +xbox-sources-2.6.7-r4.ebuild:
  Added a patch for the CAN-2004-0415 vulnerability, bug #59378.

*xbox-sources-2.6.7-r3 (21 Jul 2004)

  21 Jul 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> xbox-sources-2.4.26-r3.ebuild,
  -xbox-sources-2.6.7-r2.ebuild, +xbox-sources-2.6.7-r3.ebuild,
  +files/xbox-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0394.patch,
  +files/xbox-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0495.patch,
  +files/xbox-sources-2.4.26.CAN-2004-0535.patch,
  +files/xbox-sources-2.4.26.FPULockup-53804.patch,
  +files/xbox-sources-2.6.7.CAN-2004-0596.patch:
  Version bump for the CAN-2004-0596 issue; bug #57826. Added missing security
  fixes for 2.4 which should have been added when this ebuild was initially
  commited. Fixed header QA issue.

  19 Jul 2004; Chris Bainbridge <chrb@gentoo.org>
  xbox-sources-2.6.7-r2.ebuild:
  Added warning about broken FATX driver

